sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant B as Blazor Web App
    participant A as Auth Service
    participant P as Processing Service (GPT-4/DALL-E)
    participant S as Table Storage

    U->>B: Access /bulk-generate
    alt Not Authenticated
        B->>A: Redirect to /dev-login or OpenID
        A->>U: Login Prompt
        U->>A: Provide Credentials
        A->>B: Authenticated Session
    end

    U->>B: Trigger Bulk Generation
    B->>S: Store Request Status (Pending)
    loop For each image
        B->>P: Analyze/Generate Image
        P-->>B: Processing Result
        B->>S: Update Record (Complete/Failed)
    end
    B-->>U: Display Results
